Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Ansa na yɛbɛtoa so akɔ akyiri no, tie me kasa.

Nyinaa:
Kasa, kasa.

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Mo nyinaa asi mo bo sɛ mobɛwu mmom sen sɛ mobɛfa ɔkɔm?

Nyinaa:
Wɔasiesie. wɔasiesie no.

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Nea edi kan no, wunim sɛ Caius Marcius yɛ ɔmanfo no tamfo titiriw.

Nyinaa:
Yɛnnim, yɛnnim.

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Momma yenkum no, na yebenya atoko wɔ yɛn ankasa bo so.
So ɛnyɛ atemmu?

Nyinaa:
No more kasa wɔ on't; ma wɔnyɛ: kɔ, kɔ!

Ɔman ba a Ɔto so Abien:
Asɛmfua biako, ɔman mma pa.

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Wobu yɛn sɛ ɔman mma a wodi hia, agyanom mpanyimfo no ye.
Nea tumidi boro so no bɛma yɛn ho atɔ yɛn: sɛ wɔyɛ
bɛma yɛanya nea ɛboro so no nkutoo, bere a ɛte saa no
a ɛyɛ papa, ebia yebesusuw sɛ wɔmaa yɛn ho tɔɔ yɛn wɔ nnipa kwan so;
nanso wosusuw sɛ yɛdɔ yɛn dodo: leanness that
ɔhaw yɛn, ade a yɛrehu amane, yɛ sɛ an
inventory de kyerɛ wɔn dodow pɔtee; yɛn
amanehunu yɛ mfasoɔ ma wɔn Momma yɛmfa eyi so were
yɛn pikes, ere yɛbɛyɛ rakes: efisɛ anyame nim me
ka eyi wɔ abodoo ho kɔm mu, na ɛnyɛ aweredi ho sukɔm mu.

Ɔman ba a Ɔto so Abien:
So wobɛtoa so titiriw atia Caius Marcius?

Nyinaa:
Against him first: ɔyɛ ɔkraman paa ma commonalty.

Ɔman ba a Ɔto so Abien:
Susuw nnwuma bɛn na wayɛ ama ne man ho hwɛ?

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Eye paa; na obetumi anya abotɔyam sɛ ɔbɛma no papa
report fort, nanso sɛ ɔde ahantan tua ne ho ka.

Ɔman ba a Ɔto so Abien:
Dabi, na mmom nka adwemmɔne.

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Mese mo sɛ, deɛ wayɛ agye din no, ɔyɛeɛ
ɛde kɔ saa atirimpɔw no so: ɛwom sɛ mmarima a wɔn ahonim brɛoo betumi ayɛ saa de
abotɔyam sɛ ɔbɛka sɛ ɛyɛ ne man nti na ɔyɛɛ no
nsɔ ne maame ani na ɔde ne fã bi bɛhoahoa ne ho; a ɔno
yɛ, kosi sɛ ne suban pa no bɛkɔ soro mpo.

Ɔman ba a Ɔto so Abien:
Nea ontumi mmoa wɔ ne su mu no, wobu akontaa a
vice wɔ ne mu. Ɛnsɛ sɛ woka ɔkwan biara so sɛ ɔyɛ aniberefo.

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Sɛ ɛnsɛ sɛ meyɛ a, enhia sɛ meyɛ obonin wɔ sobo ahorow ho;
ɔwɔ mfomsoɔ, a ɛboro so, sɛ ɔbɛbrɛ wɔ mpɛn pii mu.
Nteɛteɛm bɛn na eyinom yɛ? Ɔfã foforo o' kurow no
is risen: adɛn nti na yɛtena yɛ prating ha? de kɔ Capitol no so!

Nyinaa:
Bra, bra.

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Mrɛ! hena na ɔba ha?

Ɔman ba a Ɔto so Abien:
Menenius Agripa a ɔfata; obi a ɔdɔ bere nyinaa
nkurɔfo no.

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Ɔyɛ obiako a odi nokware sɛnea ɛsɛ: so anka wɔn a wɔaka no nyinaa bɛyɛ saa!

MENENIUS: 1 .
Adwuma bɛn na, me manfo, wɔ wo nsam? ɛhe na wokɔ
Wɔde bat ne nnua a wɔde bɔ wɔn ho ban? Asɛm no? kasa, mesrɛ wo.

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Yɛn adwuma no nyɛ nea mmarahyɛ baguafo no nnim; wɔanya
na yɛahu nea yɛabɔ yɛn tirim sɛ yɛbɛyɛ wɔ dapɛn abien yi mu, .
a afei yɛbɛkyerɛ wɔn wɔ nnwuma mu. Wɔka sɛ ohiani
suitors wɔ ahome a emu yɛ den: wobehu yɛn
wɔ abasa a ɛyɛ den nso.

MENENIUS: 1 .
Adɛn nti na, awuranom, me nnamfo pa, m’afipamfo anokwafo, .
So mubeyi mo ho afi hɔ?

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Yɛrentumi, owura, yɛayɛ undone dedaw.

MENENIUS: 1 .
Meka kyerɛ mo, nnamfo, adɔe hwɛ dodow no ara
Ma mo agyanom mpanyimfo no. Nea wopɛ nti, .
W’amanehunu wɔ saa ahokyere yi mu no, ebia wo nso
Fa mo poma bɔ ɔsoro sɛnea moma so no
