MENENIUS: 1 .
Bere bi wɔ hɔ a nipadua no akwaa nyinaa
Rebell'd tiaa yafunu no, saa na ɔbɔɔ no sobo:
Ɛno te sɛ po no mu nkutoo na ɛkaa hɔ ampa
Me' nipadua no mfinimfini, meyɛ hwee na menyɛ adwuma, .
Ɔda so ara yɛ viand no cupboarding, na ensoa da
Te sɛ adwuma a wɔne wɔn a aka no yɛ, baabi a nnwinnade afoforo no
Did huu na ɔtee, yɛɛ nhyehyɛe, kyerɛkyerɛɛ, nantew, tee nka, .
Na, mo nyinaa de mo ho bɛhyɛ mu, yɛɛ ɔsom adwuma
Kɔ akɔnnɔ ne ɔdɔ a abu so no so
Nipadua no nyinaa ho. Yafunu no buae-- .

Ɔman ba a Odi Kan:
Wiɛ, owura, mmuae bɛn na ɛmaa yafunu no bae?

MENENIUS: 1 .
Owura, mɛka akyerɛ wo. Ɔde serew bi, .
Nea ne'er amfi ahurututu mu, nanso mpo saa-- .
Efisɛ, hwɛ wo, ebia mɛma yafunu no aserew
Sɛnea ɛte biara no--ɛde fɛwdi buae
Wɔ asɔremma a wɔn ani nnye ho no fam no, afã horow a atuatew no
Ɛno maa n’ani bere ne krataa a ogyee no; mpo saa na ɛfata sen biara
Sɛnea wobɔ yɛn senators ho asɛmmɔne wɔ saa asɛm no ho no
Wɔnte sɛ wo.

